  "description": "MCP server for rememori — persistent semantic memory for Claude Code and any MCP-capable agent.",
  "keywords": ["mcp", "model-context-protocol", "ai", "agent", "memory", "rememori", "claude"],
  "license": "MIT",
  "author": "Giorgio Giaffreda",
